          <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
           <a data-testid="article-link" href="/national/worst-time-of-my-life-one-woman-s-escape-from-a-spiritual-leader-20210203-p56z7s.html">
            One woman’s escape from a ‘spiritual’ leader - and what it cost her
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
           Raised in a “spiritual understanding” group many have called a cult, a young Sydney woman endured years of sexual abuse by its charismatic leader.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>

          <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
           <a data-testid="article-link" href="/culture/art-and-design/quick-sales-69m-tokens-what-it-takes-to-get-into-the-digital-art-world-20210319-p57ca7.html">
            Quick sales, $69m ‘tokens’: What it takes to get into the digital art world
           </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
           For Melbourne painter and sculptor Tom Keukenmeester the chance to sell his work in the international digital art market was enticing. But there’s a lot to consider, for artists and buyers alike, in a world in which a ‘non-fungible token’ fetches $69 million.

             </a>
            </h3>

           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/dangerfield-did-his-best-to-protect-himself-and-kelly-in-nasty-collision-says-scott-20210320-p57ck0.html">
             Dangerfield faces nervous wait over nasty collision
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            Geelong coach Chris Scott believes Patrick Dangerfield did his best to protect both himself and Jake Kelly in a brutal collision.
           </p>

         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="_3GzT4">
         <div class="_15r1L KrNcv _3R9_F" data-an-position="2" data-contentunit-parent-id="68" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">

          <div class="_1YzQk _24ZSP">
           <div class="_3XK8N">
            <h5 class="_2EuJH" data-pb-type="lb">
             Updated
            </h5>
            <h5 class="_1XJ15" data-pb-type="tg">
             <a href="/topic/afl-match-report-jfw">
              Match report
             </a>
            </h5>
           </div>
           <h3 class="_2XVos" data-pb-type="hl" data-testid="article-headline">
            <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/hawks-come-from-40-down-to-edge-bombers-with-late-goal-20210320-p57cj6.html">
             Hawks come from 40 down to edge Bombers with late goal
            </a>
           </h3>
           <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
            The AFL’s decision not to move this match from Marvel Stadium to the MCG might have denied thousands of Hawthorn fans from attending but those who were on hand enjoyed an unforgettable night.
           </p>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="_15r1L KrNcv _3R9_F" data-an-position="3" data-contentunit-parent-id="68" data-pb-type="st" data-testid="story-tile">
          <figure class="XmCQH" data-pb-type="im">
           <a data-testid="article-link" href="/sport/afl/crows-hold-off-cats-dangerfield-faces-wait-over-bump-20210320-p57cjh.html" tabindex="-1">

            </figure>
            <p class="_3XEsE" data-pb-type="ab">
             Nell Morris-Dalton is a powerful key forward and player of the future. But the 19-year-old shows strength not only on the field, but off it too.
            </p>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
        </section>
